  "detailed_description": "RoboSync is an immersive puzzle game that puts your logical thinking skills and precision to the test.<br><br>In each level, you'll find robots moving in unsynchronized patterns. Your mission? Time the release and blockage of passages just right, coordinating your robots' movements to unlock all the locks simultaneously. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761130/extras/e9f082199688f622c7720845c62cb9b0.poster.avif?t=1740757010\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761130/extras/e9f082199688f622c7720845c62cb9b0.webm?t=1740757010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761130/extras/e9f082199688f622c7720845c62cb9b0.mp4?t=1740757010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>It's crucial to carefully consider every move, executing commands precisely to achieve flawless synchronization. With progressively challenging levels, the game introduces new mechanics to keep the experience engaging.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761130/extras/99de8636c40fe90b261883d720f746f5.poster.avif?t=1740757010\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761130/extras/99de8636c40fe90b261883d720f746f5.webm?t=1740757010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761130/extras/99de8636c40fe90b261883d720f746f5.mp4?t=1740757010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Solve the challenges swiftly to earn the coveted 3 stars and attain impeccable synchronization for a special medal in each level. Get ready for an exhilarating journey where your mental agility will be constantly challenged.\"<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761130/extras/56e4efdefba20c4ee6fe314a66d7c611.poster.avif?t=1740757010\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761130/extras/56e4efdefba20c4ee6fe314a66d7c611.webm?t=1740757010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761130/extras/56e4efdefba20c4ee6fe314a66d7c611.mp4?t=1740757010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
